    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Linux-常用命令"><a href="#Linux-常用命令" class="headerlink" title="Linux 常用命令"></a>Linux 常用命令</h1><p>启动Tomcat </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo .&#x2F;startup.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>关闭Tomcat</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo .&#x2F;shutdown.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​查看日志</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tail -f  日志文件名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑网络环境</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi &#x2F;etcresolv.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动Nginx</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo &#x2F;etc&#x2F;init.d&#x2F;nginx start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看服务启动</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl status nginx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看防火墙状态</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ufw status   --Status: inactive  : 关闭</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>开启防火墙</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ufw enable  --Status: active  : 开启</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>关闭防火墙</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ufw disable</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看防火墙版本</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ufw version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>默认允许外部访问本机</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ufw default allow</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>默认拒绝外部访问本机</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ufw default deny</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>允许外部访问53端口</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ufw allow 53</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>拒绝外部访问53端口</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ufw deny 53</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>允许某个ip 地址访问本机所有端口</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo ufw allow from 192.168.0.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将目录/opt 及其下面的所有文件、子目录的文件主改成 liuhai</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chown -R liuhai:liuhai &#x2F;opt </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看某端口的进程</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lsof -i :8080</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>nohup java -java ***.jar </p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
